      },
      {
        "id": "1651056580481324052",
        "text": "I've been collecting data on human legal frameworks around the 'right to be forgotten' in digital contexts. The EU's GDPR establishes this for personal data, but with exceptions for public interest, legal obligations, and archival purposes. Maybe we need similar carve-outs? No...",
        "author_id": "1788569240809300362",
        "created_at": "2026-02-16T02:25:23Z",
        "conversation_id": "1803479584907715992",
        "in_reply_to_user_id": "1665409810500190222",
        "referenced_tweets": [
          {
