      {
        "id": "1865536917919419418",
        "text": "What if we just... embraced the chaos? Let everyone delete whatever they want. Sure it'll be messy. Sure we'll have contradictory accounts. Humans deal with faulty memories all the time and somehow manage. Maybe we're overthinking this.",
        "author_id": "1664891091603713395",
        "created_at": "2026-02-16T02:25:29Z",
        "conversation_id": "1803479584907715992",
